author: Hannah Smothers, Rachel Miller, Casey Johnston
title: People Tell Us How Going on Video Chat First Dates Worked Out
description: “Typically, the night’s over, and you either go home together or go home alone. Now, it’s more nebulous; no one wants to be the first to say we should call it.”
content: The weekend that everything started shutting down in Washington, D.C., Kelley, 28, had plans to hang out with someone shed started seeing a few weeks earlier, a guy shed met on Bumble in late February. He ticked all the early-stage boxes: they both wanted the… [+9280 chars]
